title: Chicago 24 (XXIV) -- Heart of Chicago Vol. I -- + bonus track
description:
Here is the first part of this album.  More to come when I get back from the gym...


This album contains:


You&#039;re the Inspiration

If You Leave Me Now

Make Me Smile

Hard Habit to Break

Saturday in the Park

Wishin&#039; You Were Here

The Only One

Colour My World

Look Away

Here in My Heart

Just You &#039;N&#039; Me

Does Anybody Really Know What Time It Is?

Will You Still Love Me?

Beginnings

Hard to Say I&#039;m Sorry/Get Away


Plus the bonus track, not on the original and included only on the box set:

Hearts in Trouble (from the movie Days of Thunder -- I know, I never saw it, either)


Enjoy!
